title: After a lacklustre 2023, will 2024 be a year of mega-caps?
description: Mega stocks such as HDFC Bank, Reliance Industries, ICICI Bank, Infosys, TCS, Axis Bank and Kotak Mahindra Bank, which collectively account for 48% of the total Nifty 50 weightage, have given return of 9.58% in 2023 compared with the Nifty 50's return of 20%.
